Domain Name System is how your device knows where to find the websites you want to visit. Unfortunately, most of the Internet still uses unencrypted DNS, which puts your browsing history at risk of being spied on. When enabled, Full AdBlock VPN is forcing your device to connect only to encrypted DNS servers (also called DNS over HTTPS).

Your device is connecting through our secure VPN servers, and all communication coming from, or to, your device is being encrypted using strong algorithms. This protects your personal information, like banking details or personal photos, from being stolen in unsecure places, like a coffee shop WiFi.

Full AdBlock VPN is the popular ad blocker and privacy app for Android and iOS. It\'s being supported and actively developed by the amazing open source community.
Full AdBlock VPN, the ad blocker

If you want to efficiently manage ads, trackers, malware, save on your data plan, speed up your device and protect your privacy with just one application, then Full AdBlock VPN is for you. It is free, secure and open source.
Works for all apps and all browsers
Learn more about Full AdBlock VPN Plus

For ultimate privacy protection, upgrade to Full AdBlock VPN Plus and connect through our VPN. We use WireGuard®, the most advanced VPN protocol, to encrypt your network activity and hide your IP address.

\'WireGuard\' and the \'Wireguard\' logo are registered trademarks of Jason A. Donenfeld.
What information does Full AdBlock VPN keep?

Full AdBlock VPN does not track or share any of your network activity. If you use Full AdBlock VPN Plus, for technical reasons we need to collect the most minimal data required to keep the service operational. Please consult our Privacy Policy available in the top menu for details.

Full AdBlock VPN prevents apps and browsers installed on your device from sending your private data (known as tracking fingerprints) to the Internet. It also encrypts some of your network activity (DNS queries). If you need more protection, Full AdBlock VPN Plus makes your device connect through our VPN, and uses the WireGuard® protocol to encrypt your entire network traffic.
What is Full AdBlock VPN Plus?

Full AdBlock VPN Plus is our safe and modern VPN (Virtual Private Network) service. It uses WireGuard® - a fast protocol with best-in-class encryption and low battery usage. Full AdBlock VPN Plus encrypts all of your network activity in real time, giving you the highest level of protection available. You also get the popular VPN features - hide your IP address, change your location, and unblock geo-restricted content.
Do I need to upgrade to Full AdBlock VPN Plus?

No, the upgrade is optional. You may stick to the free version of Full AdBlock VPN, forever. It is a recommended upgrade if you wish to increase your privacy protection even more, or need any of the popular features VPNs provide.
What is the Full AdBlock VPN Plus refund policy?
You can get your money back within 7-days of purchasing the subscription. Contact us through any of our apps, and simply mention you want a refund.
Where is Full AdBlock VPN located?
We are based in Sweden, where privacy is handled very seriously. Our servers are available in many places around the world.
